{"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnsymbolstylelayer\/textvariableanchoroffset"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}]}],"kind":"symbol","metadata":{"externalID":"c:objc(cs)MLNSymbolStyleLayer(py)textVariableAnchorOffset","role":"symbol","title":"textVariableAnchorOffset","modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}],"roleHeading":"Instance Property","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"textVariableAnchorOffset"}],"fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"textVariableAnchorOffset"}],"symbolKind":"property"},"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"minor":3,"major":0},"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNSymbolStyleLayer\/textVariableAnchorOffset","interfaceLanguage":"occ"},"sections":[],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNSymbolStyleLayer"]]},"abstract":[{"text":"To increase the chance of placing high-priority labels on the map, you can","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"provide an array of "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"textAnchor"},{"type":"text","text":" locations, each paired with an offset value."},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"The renderer will attempt to place the label at each location, in order, before"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"moving on to the next location+offset. Use "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"textJustify: auto"},{"type":"text","text":" to choose"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"justification based on anchor position."}],"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"platforms":["iOS"],"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"@property"},{"kind":"text","text":" ("},{"text":"nonatomic","kind":"keyword"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"text":"NSExpression","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)NSExpression"},{"kind":"text","text":" * "},{"text":"textVariableAnchorOffset","kind":"identifier"},{"text":";","kind"